  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.description": "On Advanced Woodworking...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.name": "Carpentry",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.page1.text": "My latest invention was a success, but for making more complicated designs I am going to need a proper workspace.\nI should first make a carpentry bench where I can more efficiently use my hammer and saw.\nI should also be able to preserve the wood with the new oil I have extracted.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.carpentry.page1.title": "Carpentry",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.crafting1.text": "Also, its blue flowers will be a good source for the [](item://minecraft:blue_dye) that I need for my blueprints...\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.description": "On the Crop Flax...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.name": "Flax",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.page1.text": "When I found this plant and cut it down, its stems seem to be very tough.\nUpon a closer look, I can see how the stem is composed of individual fibers.\nThe strength of these fibers must be what made the stems so tough.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.flax.page1.title": "Flax",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.description": "On the simple tools I will need...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.name": "Hammer and Saw",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page1.text": "I have found that working raw materials with my bare hands is simply too limiting.\nI must first equip myself with proper tools. A simple hammer seems to be the most practical starting point: with enough force, I can crush rocks, or flatten ingots of metal into plates.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page1.title": "Hammer and Saw",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.page3.text": "Out of these plates, in turn, I can craft a sharp saw. It will allow me to cut wood with precision.",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.hammersaw.tutorial1.title": "Basic Woodworking",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.description": "On this notebook...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.name": "Research Notes",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page1.text": "The world around me is fascinating, and yet full of unanswered questions...    \nWhy does metal soften at the heat of a flame?    \nWhy does wood bend one way but snap in another?    \nBy studying why different materials and forms of energy behave and interact as they do,\nI will be able\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page1.title": "Research Notes",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page2.text": "to fully harness the potential of all the resources and energy-forms in the world.\nSo, I decided to put together this book, in which I can keep writing my notes as I learn, in one collected place.\nPerhaps in doing so, I will also gain clarity on the path forward...\nThere is so much yet to learn...\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page3.text": "To keep this book organized, I will use different kinds of pages.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page3.title": "Entry Types",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.intro.page4.text": "I will write regular entries on normal paper (a),\ndesigns for new machines on blue paper (b),\nand I will mark my main goals with the special star icon (c).\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.description": "On the Basics of Mechanical Power...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.name": "Harnessing Rotation",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.page1.text": "Rotational force seems to be the simplest form of useful work.\nWith a hand-crank I can turn axles to drive more complex machinery.    \n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.mech.page1.title": "Harnessing Rotation",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.name": "Early Fundamentals",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.description": "Design for a Research Desk",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.name": "Research Table",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.page1.text": "My next efforts should focus towards making a desk.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.research.page1.title": "Research Table",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.crafting1.text": "Perfect, with these in one hand and my hammer in the other, I will be able to make nailed wooden boards.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.description": "Design for a Roller Mill",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.name": "Roller",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.page1.text": "For more advanced woodworking, I will need small metal nails that I can drive into the planks with my hammer.\nI should make a machine capable of stretching metal ingots into rods, so that I can craft nails out of these.\nA design where the items get rolled between two cylinders would do the trick for sure.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.page1.title": "Roller",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.tutorial1.text": "I can rotate a [](item://iljatech:crank) attached to the side of the roller mill to work it.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.tutorial1.title": "Working Setup",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.roller.tutorial2.title": "Basic Woodworking",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.description": "Design for Fiber Spinning Frame",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.name": "Spinning Frame",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.page1.text": "The fibers from the flax stems almost resemble strings. I could then weave these to make cloth.\nI think it will be not only soft, but also durable, thanks to the sturdiness of these fibers.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.spinning.page1.title": "Spinning Frame",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.crafting1.text": "will press down, by applying mechanical power with the crank.\nBy releasing power it should come up again.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.description": "Design for a Squeezing Press",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.name": "Squeezer",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page1.text": "I noticed a greasy substance exists inside seeds.\nI am curious if by applying enough pressure, I can squeeze this out.\nA small machine should do the trick.\nIt should consist of a basin where I put the seeds and let the oil accumulate, and a movable plate which I\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page1.title": "Squeezer",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page2.text": "When I want to press a lot of seeds, I should repeatedly power and de-power the squeezer in an [#](FF5555)alternating[#]() way to make it go up and down.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.page2.title": "Squeezer",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.basics.squeezer.tutorial1.title": "Working Setup",
