  "book.iljatech.iljatech.pyrometallurgy.tin.description": "On the soft and pliable metal...",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.pyrometallurgy.tin.name": "Tin",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.pyrometallurgy.tin.page1.text": "I dug up some dark mineral, which appears to be rather common.\nPurifying the ore to its metallic form should be easy enough, as it needs only a little heat before it melts.\nThe material is soft and easily pliable compared to other metals.\nI am sure this will be useful, but I don't know yet for what.\n",
  "book.iljatech.iljatech.pyrometallurgy.tin.page1.title": "Tin",
